(c) every rescission of exemption from registration effected under the provisions of section twelve;
every rescission of exemption from registration effected under the provisions of section twelve;
(d) every cancellation of registration effected under the provisions of section thirteen;
every cancellation of registration effected under the provisions of section thirteen;
(e) every refusal to register under the provisions of section eight or nine; and
